entries.title_d: Deliver the satellite to the second engineer in the Endor system.
entries.title: Endor System: Sattelite Delivery - Part 2
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the second engineer's arrival location and wait for him to arrive.
entries.quest_location_d: The second engineer will meet you in the Endor system as well.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the engineer and transfer the last satellite to him. Once this is completed return to your commander for further instructions.
entries.hello_d: Good day, pilot. Thanks for dropping these off to me. I will get them set up right away.
entries.found_loc_d: Delivery location sent to your nav computer. Bring the sattelite to the field engineer in that region.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Ok, we have the sattelite. Good luck, pilot. Your commanding officer requested that you report in.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by for the field engineer ship's arrival.
